The bot popped his head up...one of his dandilions had detected
movement and had relayed the images back to his circuits....Hmm so
there is other life on the planet...He then turned from his work and
looked in that direction.....hmmm well my weeds should give him a nice
surpise...

The weed plant around the dandilion that had spotted the movment
startted to spread more and more towards the bot....
